# 世界地图

## Vue2 版本

### `map-world.vue`

```javascript
<template>
  <div>
    <div style="height:calc(100vh);">
      <RelationGraph
          ref="graphRef"
          :options="graphOptions"
          :on-node-click="onNodeClick"
          :on-line-click="onLineClick"
      >
        <template #canvas-plug>
          <!--- 可以将一些不允许被拖动的元素放在这里 --->
          <WorldMap />
        </template>
        <template #graph-plug>
          <div class="c-my-panel">
            <div style="padding:10px;">
              <el-button round type="primary" @click="saveData">保存当前图谱的内容</el-button>
            </div>
            <div class="c-snapshots">
              <div class="c-option-name">已保存的快照：</div>
              <template v-for="thisSnapshot of graphSnapshots">
                <div :key="thisSnapshot.name" class="c-snapshot-item" @click="redrawSnapshot(thisSnapshot)">{{thisSnapshot.name}}</div>
              </template>
            </div>
          </div>
        </template>
      </RelationGraph>
    </div>
  </div>
</template>

<script>
// 如果您没有在main.js文件中使用Vue.use(RelationGraph); 就需要使用下面这一行代码来引入relation-graph
// import RelationGraph from 'relation-graph';
import WorldMap from "./res-map-world.vue";
export default {
  name: 'Demo',
  components: {WorldMap},
  data() {
    return {
      mapId: 'world',
      graphSnapshots: [],
      graphOptions: {
        debug: false,
        // backgroundImage: '/images/graph-grid-bg.png',
        // backgroundColor: '#fce7d3',
        allowSwitchLineShape: true,
        allowSwitchJunctionPoint: true,
        allowShowDownloadButton: true,
        defaultJunctionPoint: 'border',
        placeOtherNodes: false,
        placeSingleNode: false,
        graphOffset_x: 0,
        graphOffset_y: 0,
        defaultNodeColor: '#f39930',
        defaultNodeBorderWidth: 1,
        defaultNodeBorderColor: '#f39930',
        defaultNodeWidth: 20,
        defaultNodeHeight: 20,
        defaultLineColor: '#f39930',
        defaultLineWidth: 2,
        layout: {
          layoutName: 'fixed'
        }
        // 这里可以参考"Graph 图谱"中的参数进行设置
      }
    };
  },
  mounted() {
    this.showGraph();
  },
  methods: {
    async showGraph() {
      const jsonData = {
        "rootId":"R",
        "nodes":[
          {"id":"R","text":"R","opacity":1,"x":570,"y":250},
          {"id":"A","text":"A","opacity":1,"x":0,"y":0},
          {"id":"B","text":"B","opacity":1,"x":0,"y":0},
          {"id":"C","text":"C","opacity":1,"x":0,"y":0},
          {"id":"D","text":"D","opacity":1,"x":0,"y":0},
            // 以下两个不可见的节点用于标记左上角和右下角，方便截图完整
          {"id":"image-from","text":"","opacity":0,x: -49, y: -20},
          {"id":"image-to","text":"","opacity":0,x: 1184, y: 652},
        ],
        "lines":[
          {from: 'R', to: 'A', animation: 1, lineShape: 3 },
          {from: 'R', to: 'B', animation: 2 },
          {from: 'R', to: 'C', animation: 3 },
          {from: 'R', to: 'D', animation: 4, lineShape: 1 },
        ]
      };
      const rootNodeJson = jsonData.nodes.find(n => n.id === jsonData.rootId);
      const rangeSize = 500;
      jsonData.nodes.forEach(node => {
        if(node.id === rootNodeJson.id)return;
        node.x = rootNodeJson.x + Math.floor(Math.random() * rangeSize) - rangeSize / 2;
        node.y = rootNodeJson.y + Math.floor(Math.random() * rangeSize) - rangeSize / 2;
      });
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      await graphInstance.setJsonData(jsonData);
      await graphInstance.moveToCenter();
    },
    onNodeClick(nodeObject, $event) {
      console.log('onNodeClick:', nodeObject.text, `x: ${nodeObject.x}, y: ${nodeObject.y}`);
    },
    onLineClick(lineObject, linkObject, $event) {
      console.log('onLineClick:', lineObject);
    },
    saveData() {
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      const allNodesWithPosition = graphInstance.getNodes().map(node => {
        return {
          id: node.id,
          text: node.text,
          x: node.x,
          y: node.y,
          opacity: node.opacity
        }
      });
      const allLines = graphInstance.getLinks().reduce((currentLines, link) => {
        const {from,to,lineShape,animation} = link.relations[0];
        return currentLines.concat([{from,to,lineShape,animation}])
      }, []);
      const graphSnapshotData = {
        rootId: graphInstance.graphData.rootNode.id,
        nodes: allNodesWithPosition,
        lines: allLines,
      }
      if (this.graphSnapshots.length > 0 && JSON.stringify(graphSnapshotData) === JSON.stringify(this.graphSnapshots[this.graphSnapshots.length - 1].data)) {
        alert('The data has not changed');
        return;
      }
      this.graphSnapshots.push({
        name: new Date().toLocaleTimeString(),
        data: graphSnapshotData
      });
    },
    redrawSnapshot(theSnapshot) {
      const graphInstance = this.$refs.graphRef.getInstance();
      graphInstance.setJsonData(theSnapshot.data);
    }
  }
};

</script>
```

### `map-world.vue`

```javascript
<template>
  <div>
    <div style="height:calc(100vh);">
      <RelationGraph

          ref="graphRef"
          :options="graphOptions"
          :on-node-click="onNodeClick"
          :on-line-click="onLineClick"
      >
        <template #canvas-plug>
          <!--- You can put some elements that are not allowed to be dragged here --->
          <WorldMap />
        </template>
        <template #graph-plug>
          <div class="c-my-panel">
            <div style="padding:10px;">
              <el-button round type="primary" @click="saveData">Save the content of the current graph</el-button>
            </div>
            <div class="c-snapshots">
              <div class="c-option-name">Saved snapshots:</div>
              <template v-for="thisSnapshot of graphSnapshots" :key="thisSnapshot.name">
                <div class="c-snapshot-item" @click="redrawSnapshot(thisSnapshot)">{{thisSnapshot.name}}</div>
              </template>
            </div>
          </div>
        </template>
      </RelationGraph>
    </div>
  </div>
</template>

<script lang="ts" setup>
import { ref, onMounted } from 'vue';
import WorldMap from "./res-map-world.vue";
import RelationGraph from 'relation-graph-vue3';
import type { RGJsonData, RGNode, RGLine, RGLink, RGUserEvent, RGOptions, RelationGraphComponent } from 'relation-graph-vue3';

const graphRef = ref<RelationGraphComponent>();
const graphSnapshots = ref([]);
const graphOptions: RGOptions = {
    debug: false,
    allowSwitchLineShape: true,
    allowSwitchJunctionPoint: true,
    allowShowDownloadButton: true,
    defaultJunctionPoint: 'border',
    placeOtherNodes: false,
    placeSingleNode: false,
    graphOffset_x: 0,
    graphOffset_y: 0,
    defaultNodeColor: '#f39930',
    defaultNodeBorderWidth: 1,
    defaultNodeBorderColor: '#f39930',
    defaultNodeWidth: 20,
    defaultNodeHeight: 20,
    defaultLineColor: '#f39930',
    defaultLineWidth: 2,
    layout: {
        layoutName: 'fixed'
    }
};

onMounted(async () => {
    await showGraph();
});

const showGraph = async () => {
    const jsonData: RGJsonData = {
        rootId: 'R',
        nodes: [
            { "id": "R", "text": "R", "opacity": 1, "x": 570, "y": 250 },
            { "id": "A", "text": "A", "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
            { "id": "B", "text": "B", "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
            { "id": "C", "text": "C", "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
            { "id": "D", "text": "D", "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
            { "id": "image-from", "text": "", "opacity": 0, x: -49, y: -20 },
            { "id": "image-to", "text": "", "opacity": 0, x: 1184, y: 652 },
        ],
        "lines": [
            { from: 'R', to: 'A', animation: 1, lineShape: 3 },
            { from: 'R', to: 'B', animation: 2 },
            { from: 'R', to: 'C', animation: 3 },
            { from: 'R', to: 'D', animation: 4, lineShape: 1 },
        ]
    };
    const rootNodeJson = jsonData.nodes.find(n => n.id === jsonData.rootId);
    const rangeSize = 500;
    jsonData.nodes.forEach(node => {
        if (node.id === rootNodeJson.id) return;
        node.x = rootNodeJson.x + Math.floor(Math.random() * rangeSize) - rangeSize / 2;
        node.y = rootNodeJson.y + Math.floor(Math.random() * rangeSize) - rangeSize / 2;
    });
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    await graphInstance.setJsonData(jsonData);
    await graphInstance.moveToCenter();
};

const onNodeClick = (nodeObject: RGNode, $event: RGUserEvent) => {
    console.log('onNodeClick:', nodeObject.text, `x: ${nodeObject.x}, y: ${nodeObject.y}`);
};

const onLineClick = (lineObject: RGLine, linkObject: RGLink, $event: RGUserEvent) => {
    console.log('onLineClick:', lineObject);
};

const saveData = () => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    const allNodesWithPosition = graphInstance.getNodes().map(node => {
        return {
            id: node.id,
            text: node.text,
            x: node.x,
            y: node.y,
            opacity: node.opacity

        }
    });
    const allLines = graphInstance.getLinks().reduce((currentLines, link) => {
        const { from, to, lineShape, animation } = link.relations[0];
        return currentLines.concat([{ from, to, lineShape, animation }])
    }, []);
    const graphSnapshotData: RGJsonData = {
        rootId: graphInstance.graphData.rootNode.id,
        nodes: allNodesWithPosition,
        lines: allLines,
    }
    if (graphSnapshots.value.length > 0 && JSON.stringify(graphSnapshotData) === JSON.stringify(graphSnapshots.value[graphSnapshots.value.length - 1].data)) {
        alert('The data has not changed');
        return;
    }
    graphSnapshots.value.push({
        name: new Date().toLocaleTimeString(),
        data: graphSnapshotData

    });
};

const redrawSnapshot = (theSnapshot) => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.value!.getInstance();
    graphInstance.setJsonData(theSnapshot.data);
};
</script>
```

## React 版本

### `map-world.tsx`

```javascript
import React, {useRef, useEffect, useState} from 'react';
import
  RelationGraph, { RGJsonData, RGNode, RGLine, RGLink, RGUserEvent, RGOptions, RelationGraphComponent }
  from 'relation-graph-react';
import './map-world.scss';
import WorldMap from './res-map-world';
import {MyLinkButton} from "./RGDemoComponents/MyUIComponents";

const MapWorld = () => {
  const graphRef = useRef<RelationGraphComponent|null>(null);
  const [graphSnapshots, setGraphSnapshots] = useState([]);
  const graphOptions: RGOptions = {
    debug: false,
    allowSwitchLineShape: true,
    allowSwitchJunctionPoint: true,
    allowShowDownloadButton: true,
    defaultJunctionPoint: 'border',
    placeOtherNodes: false,
    placeSingleNode: false,
    graphOffset_x: 0,
    graphOffset_y: 0,
    defaultNodeColor: '#f39930',
    defaultNodeBorderWidth: 1,
    defaultNodeBorderColor: '#f39930',
    defaultNodeWidth: 20,
    defaultNodeHeight: 20,
    defaultLineColor: '#f39930',
    defaultLineWidth: 2,
    layout: {
      layoutName: 'fixed'
    }
  };

  useEffect(() => {
    showGraph();
  }, []);

  const showGraph = async () => {
    const jsonData: RGJsonData = {
      rootId: 'R',
      nodes: [
        { "id": "R", "text": "R", "opacity": 1, "x": 570, "y": 250 },
        { "id": "A", "text": "A", "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
        { "id": "B", "text": "B", "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
        { "id": "C", "text": "C", "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
        { "id": "D", "text": "D", "opacity": 1, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
        { "id": "image-from", "text": "", "opacity": 0, x: -49, y: -20 },
        { "id": "image-to", "text": "", "opacity": 0, x: 1184, y: 652 },
      ],
      "lines": [
        { from: 'R', to: 'A', animation: 1, lineShape: 3 },
        { from: 'R', to: 'B', animation: 2 },
        { from: 'R', to: 'C', animation: 3 },
        { from: 'R', to: 'D', animation: 4, lineShape: 1 },
      ]
    };
    const rootNodeJson = jsonData.nodes.find(n => n.id === jsonData.rootId);
    const rangeSize = 500;
    jsonData.nodes.forEach(node => {
      if (node.id === rootNodeJson.id) return;
      node.x = rootNodeJson.x + Math.floor(Math.random() * rangeSize) - rangeSize / 2;
      node.y = rootNodeJson.y + Math.floor(Math.random() * rangeSize) - rangeSize / 2;
    });
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    await graphInstance.setJsonData(jsonData);
    await graphInstance.moveToCenter();
  };

  const onNodeClick = (nodeObject: RGNode, $event: RGUserEvent) => {
    console.log('onNodeClick:', nodeObject.text, `x: ${nodeObject.x}, y: ${nodeObject.y}`);
  };

  const onLineClick = (lineObject: RGLine, linkObject: RGLink, $event: RGUserEvent) => {
    console.log('onLineClick:', lineObject);
  };

  const saveData = () => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    const allNodesWithPosition = graphInstance.getNodes().map(node => {
      return {
        id: node.id,
        text: node.text,
        x: node.x,
        y: node.y,
        opacity: node.opacity

      }
    });
    const allLines = graphInstance.getLinks().reduce((currentLines, link) => {
      const { from, to, lineShape, animation } = link.relations[0];
      return currentLines.concat([{ from, to, lineShape, animation }])
    }, []);
    const graphSnapshotData: RGJsonData = {
      rootId: graphInstance.graphData.rootNode.id,
      nodes: allNodesWithPosition,
      lines: allLines,
    }
    if (graphSnapshots.length > 0 && JSON.stringify(graphSnapshotData) === JSON.stringify(graphSnapshots[graphSnapshots.length - 1].data)) {
      alert('The data has not changed');
      return;
    }
    setGraphSnapshots([{
      name: new Date().toLocaleTimeString(),
      data: graphSnapshotData
    }].concat(graphSnapshots));
  };

  const redrawSnapshot = (theSnapshot) => {
    const graphInstance = graphRef.current!.getInstance();
    graphInstance.setJsonData(theSnapshot.data);
  };

  return (
    <div>
      <div style={{ height: '100vh' }}>
        <div className="c-my-panel rounded-lg absolute left-20 top-20 z-20 p-4 bg-white border-solid border-2 border-black shadow-lg">
          <div style={{ padding: '10px' }}>
            <MyLinkButton onClick={saveData}>Save the content of the current graph</MyLinkButton>
          </div>
          <div className="c-snapshots">
            <div className="c-option-name">Saved snapshots:</div>
            {graphSnapshots.map(thisSnapshot => (
              <div className="c-snapshot-item" onClick={() => redrawSnapshot(thisSnapshot)} key={thisSnapshot.name}>{thisSnapshot.name}</div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <RelationGraph
          ref={graphRef}
          options={graphOptions}
          onNodeClick={onNodeClick}
          onLineClick={onLineClick}
        >
          <div>
            {/* You can put some elements that are not allowed to be dragged here */}
            <WorldMap />
          </div>
        </RelationGraph>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

export default MapWorld;
```

```javascript
import React from "react";

export interface MySelectorProps {
  small?: boolean
  currentValue: string|number
  data:{value: string|number, text:string}[]
  onChange: (newValue:string|number, label:string) => void
}
export const MySelector:React.FC<MySelectorProps> = ({small, data, onChange, currentValue}) => {
  return (
    <div className="flex flex-wrap justify-center rounded-lg border border-gray-900 overflow-hidden">
      {
        data.map(item =>
          <div key={item.value}
               className={`border-r w-auto text-xs cursor-pointer whitespace-nowrap ${currentValue === item.value && 'bg-blue-500 text-white'} ${small?' px-2 h-6 leading-6':'h-8 px-3 leading-8'}`}
               onClick={() => {onChange(item.value, item.text);}}
          >
          {item.text}
        </div>)
      }
    </div>
  );
};
export interface MySwitchProps {
  currentValue: boolean
  onChange: (newValue:boolean) => void
}
export const MySwitch:React.FC<MySwitchProps> = ({onChange, currentValue}) => {
  return (
    <div className={`w-14 flex rounded-full border p-0.5 ${currentValue ? 'justify-end border-blue-500' : 'justify-start border-gray-500'}`}>
      <div
        className={`w-8 h-5 leading-8 rounded-full w-auto px-3 text-xs cursor-pointer whitespace-nowrap ${currentValue ? 'bg-blue-500' : 'bg-gray-500'}`} onClick={() => {onChange(!currentValue);}}>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};
export interface MySliderProps {
  min: number
  max: number
  step: number
  currentValue: number
  onChange: (newValue:number) => void
}
export const MySlider:React.FC<MySliderProps> = ({min, max, step, currentValue, onChange}) => {
  return (
    <div>
      <input
        type="range"
        className="w-72"
        min={min}
        max={max}
        step={step}
        value={currentValue}
        onChange={(e) => { onChange(parseFloat(e.target.value))}}
      />
    </div>
  );
};

export interface MyRangeSliderProps {
  min: number
  max: number
  step: number
  currentValue: [number, number]
  onChange: (newValue:[number, number]) => void
}
export const MyRangeSlider:React.FC<MyRangeSliderProps> = ({min, max, step, currentValue, onChange}) => {
  return (
    <div className="w-72">
      <div>Min:</div>
      <input
        type="range"
        className="w-full"
        min={min}
        max={max}
        step={step}
        value={currentValue[0]}
        onChange={(e) => { if (parseFloat(e.target.value) < currentValue[1]) onChange([parseFloat(e.target.value), currentValue[1]])}}
      />
      <div>Max:</div>
      <input
        type="range"
        className="w-full"
        min={min}
        max={max}
        step={step}
        value={currentValue[1]}
        onChange={(e) => { if (parseFloat(e.target.value) > currentValue[0]) onChange([currentValue[0], parseFloat(e.target.value)])}}
      />
    </div>
  );
};
export interface MyButtonProps {
  onClick: () => void
  disabled?: boolean
}
export const MyButton:React.FC<MyButtonProps> = ({children, onClick, disabled}) => {
  return (
    <button className={`mr-2 px-2 py-1 rounded ${disabled===true ? 'bg-gray-300 text-black cursor-not-allowed':'bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white'}`}
            onClick={()=>{onClick();}}>{children}</button>
  );
};
export interface MyLinkButtonProps {
  onClick: () => void
}
export const MyLinkButton:React.FC<MyLinkButtonProps> = ({children, onClick}) => {
  return (
    <div className="text-blue-600 cursor-pointer underline decoration-1" onClick={()=>{onClick();}}>
      {children}
    </div>
  );
};
export interface MyCheckBoxProps {
  currentValue: string|number
  data:{value: string|number, text:string}[]
```
